divs: sighting detailsafter reviewing the pictures i took earlier on the same day at the laguna beach, one picture caught my attention as i saw an unidentified object captured on the background. it was interesting since no one at the scene when i was taking this picture saw it. other pictures i took at the same location did not have this object either. please see below for more information: 1) i took this photo at laguna beach on october 12th, 2010 3:01 pm 2) i have first noticed this object when i was reviewing the pictures i took, which was the same day. 3) i could not relate this object to anything i know. 4) na - i do not kknow how its actions\motions were since it was only taken in one picture. the picture i took approximately 4 seconds later did not have this object on the background. 5) i have a mixed feeling as i think i took a picture of ufo! 6) the object was appeared on only one out of all the pictures i took that day.
